0. Introduction
This is a 3D gesture based user interface library. It contains the following building blocks:
     1. Gesture Recognition Engine
     	A generic gesture recognizer that takes a set of training samples of 3D gestures. With proper
	training, the user could use the learned classifier to recognize the gesture input which will
	be used to interact with 3D (or 2D) objects.

     2.	Smart Object Interface
     	The object in the environment should be smart enough to interact with the gesture input by the 
	user in order to foster smooth user experience. 	
